# {{defdate|from 1588}} {{q|by extension from the [[fist]] of a [[falconer]]}} [[huntsmanship]], [[hunting]] [[ability]]
# {{alt sp|ja|辛夷|tr=kobushi|t={{vern|Kobushi magnolia}}, {{taxlink|Magnolia kobus|species}}}}

